  "detailed_description": "<h1>Comparative Grid</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/0366b19072ccf437e6f76552df1f1deb.avif?t=1772557241\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><br><h1>Ultimate Edition</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/edf2b1dff42ec73399f593eaf0d75151.avif?t=1772557241\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>TOM CLANCY’S THE DIVISION 2 ULTIMATE EDITION INCLUDES:<br><br>· The base game;<br>· The Warlords of New York expansion;<br>· The Battle for Brooklyn DLC;<br>· 1,000 Bonus Premium Credits;<br>· A level 40 boost, allowing you to jump into the Battle for Brooklyn campaign;<br>· Stash space increase;<br>· All six endgame Specializations instantly unlocked;<br>· Eight exclusive missions;<br>· The Battleworn Secret Service Pack;<br>· The First Responder Pack;<br>· The Elite Agent Pack;<br>· One exclusive emote and outfit.</p><br><h1>Gold Edition</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/43b4d4a752cd56c7b79e39b08232f31a.avif?t=1772557241\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><br><br>TOM CLANCY’S THE DIVISION 2 GOLD EDITION INCLUDES:<br><br>· The base game;<br>· The Warlords of New York expansion;<br>· The Battle for Brooklyn DLC;<br>· A level 40 boost, allowing you to jump into the Battle for Brooklyn campaign;<br>· Stash space increase.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Defend and rebuild Washington, D.C. after a devastating pandemic in this tactical open world third-person shooter:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TACTICAL COMBAT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/148a120980b159cd8923fef7fccfb4bf.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/148a120980b159cd8923fef7fccfb4bf.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/148a120980b159cd8923fef7fccfb4bf.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Engage enemies in intense, cover-based firefights where tactical positioning and utility usage make the difference between life and death.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUILD THE ULTIMATE AGENT</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/fdaf7df9fe1484ea1649a2a21545c853.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/fdaf7df9fe1484ea1649a2a21545c853.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/fdaf7df9fe1484ea1649a2a21545c853.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Loot and craft cutting-edge gear and learn powerful skills to customize the way you fight. Take things further with Specializations, with roles like the long-range marksman, the demolition expert, the survivalist leader, and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TEAMWORK SAVES LIVES</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Team up with up to three other agents for tactical co-op missions where synergy matters. Combine Specializations, share resources, and take on dynamic challenges that scale with your squad.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE EVER-EVOLVING WASHINGTON, D.C.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>From tense firefights in changing weather to the constant push and pull of factions warring over map control, the city reacts, adapts, and challenges you to survive with every move you make.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VISCERAL ENDGAME</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/5b71e6eade9033d27823456aff15e57a.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/5b71e6eade9033d27823456aff15e57a.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/5b71e6eade9033d27823456aff15e57a.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Reaching max level is just the start. Dive into high-stakes endgame missions, intense PvP battles, and dynamic world events that push your skills and teamwork to the limit. Every season brings fresh rewards and fierce challenges.",
