ai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/75289faeadbb3622410780aba911ad57.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Team up with up to three other agents for tactical co-op missions where synergy matters. Combine Specializations, share resources, and take on dynamic challenges that scale with your squad.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SURVIVE EVER-EVOLVING WASHINGTON, D.C.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.webm?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/3d622aa311d0252311dda92da1e764ed.mp4?t=1772557241\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>From tense firefights in changing weather to the constant push and pull of factions warring over map control, the city reacts, adapts, and challenges you to survive with every move you make.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VISCERAL ENDGAME</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/5b71e6eade9033d27823456aff15e57a.poster.avif?t=1772557241\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2221490/extras/5b71e6eade9033d27823456aff